@Embeddable @VoDml(id="caom2:types.Interval", role=dataType) public class Interval extends Object implements org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulations
a set of numeric values defined by a lower and upper bound (bounds included: [a,b]). dataType: Interval
